'''''Aval Mella Sirithal''''' ({{lit|She smiled gently}}) is a [[1987 in film|1987]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by M. N. Jai Sundar for Sri Kavitha Cine Arts. The film stars [[Murali (Tamil actor)|Murali]], [[Seetha (actress)|Seetha]] and [[Madhuri (Tamil actress)|Madhuri]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Aval Mella Sirithal LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/111/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425035818/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F111%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=25 April 2014|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

