Soundtrack was composed by Gangai Amaran.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bollywoodvinyl.in/collections/kannada-malayalam-telugu-tamil-lps/products/aval-mella-siriththal-1987-tamil-bollywood-vinyl-lp |title=Aval Mella Siriththal 1987 - Tamil Bollywood Vinyl LP |website=''Bollywood Vinyl'' |access-date=2019-06-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/aval-mella-sirithaal-orignal-motion-picture-soundtrack-ep/1458067121 |title=Aval Mella Sirithaal songs |website=''[[Apple Music]]'' |access-date=2019-06-06}}</ref>
